{"tid":2105851,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白宮顧問納瓦羅 : 預期總統川普會對TikTok與微信等應用程式採強硬行動","createTime":"2020-07-13T02:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T04:05:03.000Z","uid":28765,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"11c02dd2f2cf1134907f44017321b7a6713dee2e","tid":2105851,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T02:30:27.000Z","msg":"（中央社舊金山12日綜合外電報導）華盛頓與北京緊張關係升高，美國白宮貿易顧問納瓦洛（Peter Navarro）今天表示，預期總統川普會對TikTok與微信（Wechat）等應用程式祭出強硬行動。<br />\n<br />\n川普上週表示，為懲罰中國處置2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19）疫情不力，考慮禁止短影音平台TikTok。<br />\n<br />\n納瓦洛今天接受福斯新聞（Fox News）訪問時主張，美國人必須了解「資料進入那些給孩子們莫大歡樂的行動應用程式...就會直接進入中國的伺服器，直接給中國軍方、中國共產黨」。<br />\n<br />\n他說，這些應用程式可用以竊取智慧財產，「所以預期」川普會對此採取強硬行動。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n隸屬騰訊旗下的微信用戶則超過10億。<br />\n<br />\n納瓦洛也指控TikTok的新老闆、也就是迪士尼串流平台前負責人梅爾（Kevin Mayer）只是一個傀儡。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n（譯者：鄭詩韻/核稿：陳亦偉）1090713<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202007130025.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202007130025.aspx&d=Z5C23SoLFrdwUrTWaDZos20Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=ddc2d77c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202007130025.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n禁抖音都算 美國咁撚多中國人禁微信就好睇囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2453a6e99577fe75a9dd7a40e2b484b5803d35","tid":2105851,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T02:59:07.000Z","msg":"我都預期左佢會簽香港自治法架喎  咪就係等左十日都未簽囉所以<br />\n算鳩數啦黃豆侵  撚有膽咩  就算肯做  都只係虎頭蛇尾  雷聲大雨點少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"345b752d29a7b83753f492c2078c02c5ef776142","tid":2105851,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:11:36.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62989c2a73946b924f335d11f173cc051c19a6da","tid":2105851,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:33:15.000Z","msg":"又放風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f067c05156455035a1f55b1573fab4800e2e33","tid":2105851,"uid":267494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:41:19.000Z","msg":"禁埋wechat pay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3980fba66168aa67fdd6ac3960dd25c30a856fcd","tid":2105851,"uid":143343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:46:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d22ff6cad048c3e279dd20faaf3b976cfd89b4f1","tid":2105851,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:55:07.000Z","msg":"終於搞QQ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf494e7c96a458611cba3c7bdd428045d4ace49","tid":2105851,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T04:03:12.000Z","msg":"基本上我見係美國d中國人冇人唔用微信 <br />\n<br />\n而且一得閒就不停講/睇微信d on9片<br />\n<br />\n如果話禁唔知會發癲成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bdf8f33633849b78530371f56b3d424c1c282f8","tid":2105851,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdf494e7c96a458611cba3c7bdd428045d4ace49","tid":2105851,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T04:03:12.000Z","msg":"基本上我見係美國d中國人冇人唔用微信 <br />\n<br />\n而且一得閒就不停講/睇微信d on9片<br />\n<br />\n如果話禁唔知會發癲成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T04:05:03.000Z","msg":"話係佢地精神支柱都唔誇張<br />\n<br />\n特別係d中老年個班 岩岩呢幾年先識用智能電話用到上晒癮"}]}